	<div id="content" class="hfeed">
	<article class="post-604653 post type-post status-publish hentry category-mergers-acquisitions category-telecommunications tag-altice-sa tag-antitrust-laws-and-competition-issues tag-bouygues tag-bouygues-martin tag-cable-television tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-sfr tag-vivendi-universal tag-wireless-communications per-bouygues-martin des-antitrust-laws-and-competition-issues des-cable-television des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures des-wireless-communications org-altice-sa org-bouygues org-sfr org-vivendi-universal" id="post-604653">
